<ab>Herspruck </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> frewnde, uns hat fürgelegt Weigel Graser,
                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, wie im Margret Hawheinczlin, ewr
                <expan>mitb<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>in</expan>, seine güt auf die
                <expan>lantschran<ex>n</ex></expan> czü Sulczbach <expan>gelad<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
            hab, <add>die doch kein recht von dem <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> an uns
                  <expan>gevord<ex>er</ex>t</expan> hat, das wir ir <expan>v<ex>er</ex>sagt</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan></add>. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                <expan>diselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>mitb<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>in</expan> daran weisen wöllet, daz sie von der klag
            auf <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>lantschran<ex>n</ex></expan> lazz und die abtü. Het sie
              <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> czü <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> iht <expan>czesprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, darumb wöllen
            wir ir <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ire<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>scheimbot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit <expan>ire<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalt <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czog<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>slewnig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> hellffen, wenn wir dir des ermant, so
              <expan>d<ex>er</ex>selb</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> anheim ist. Und <add>sagt uns auch
                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> daz das <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> sache
                  <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> sey, die in <expan>selb<ex>er</ex></expan> nicht
              antreffen, sunder es sey von kind <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, die waisen sein, der
              vormund er von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> ist. <expan>Davo<ex>n</ex></expan></add> getrawen
              <add>wir</add> ew wol, ir weiset sie also. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.
                <expan>Antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Urba<ex>n</ex>i</expan>.</ab>
</div>
